Year : 1999 Country : USA Language : English Genre : Obuchyuschee video Duration : 0:48 


Description : Sunburst Finishing The art of Applying A traditional sunburst. Don uses special color-matching boards to duplicate a vintage guitar finish. You'll learn how to make your own color boards, how to mix custom lacquer shaders, and how to spray sealers, toner coats and clear lacquer topcoats. Techniques for wet-sanding, rub-out and pedestal buffing are demonstrated, too. 50 minutes.
